  "description": {
    "zh": "啊，你来了，捍卫者！希望你状态依旧。你的事情我听说了，就黑哨，你强得可怕就给踢出竞技场。这帮垃圾。\n\n但你还是有我和我的弟兄们的！下次有空我带你打派（APEX）。只不过最近我的清理小队损失惨重————人倒是没事，就是装备都打烂了，修都不好修！\n\n你打JJC是赚钱，找我也是一样嘛，所以何不来我这搭把手呢？找些插板，每种都来几块，这里来点“granit”板，那里来点“SAPI”板，应该没难度吧。\n其实你记不住可以拿个笔在“愿望清单”上面标记一下，这样看到了就不会忽略了。",
    "en": "Ah there you are champion! I hope you're still in shape, I heard what happened. A shame that you were banished from the Arena...\n\nBut there are still ways you can help me and my guys out! Most of the cleanup crew got messed up lately, not many of them were killed but their gear was damaged so badly that it's absolutely unusable now, not even repairable!\n\nI know you love making money, so why don't you lend a hand here? Find some armor plates, a few of each type, granit plates here, sapi plates there, shouldn't be too difficult for a warrior like you.\nI hope I don't get disappointed, ha!"
  },
